Revision history for IO-Async-Loop-linux

0.04    CHANGES:
         * Updated to look for IO::Async::Loop::Ppoll instead of ::IO_Ppoll

0.03    CHANGES:
         * Various updates to keep CPANTS happy

0.02    CHANGES:
         * Use Module::Build's "recommends" keyword to recommend
           IO::Async::Loop::Epoll

0.01    First version, released on an unsuspecting world.

